.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, subway, boat, roller
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person driving the boat##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| Transport         | jet-ski | roller | subway   | boat |

