.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
House: palace, futuristic, cottage, ranch-style
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the futuristic house is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the palace house is between the person driving the bus and the cottage house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| House   | ranch-style   | futuristic | palace | cottage      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

