.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, videographer
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod, palace, colonial
1. the librarian is between the gothic-revival house and the dressmaker##2
2. the colonial house is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the dressmaker is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | entrepreneur | librarian | dressmaker | videographer |
| House   | gothic-revival         | colonial       | cape-cod    | palace         |

