.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, mechanic, analyst, coach
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the coach##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the musician is on the right of the mechanic##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the mechanic and the person who's sport is tennis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Job    | coach   | analyst      | mechanic   | musician  |
| Sport   | tennis | ice-hockey | swimming | baseball |

