.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, lime, onion
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, november, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating onion and the person eating apple##2
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | cauliflower | onion   | lime        |
| Birthday   | july | november   | may | september |

