.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, rock-climbing, singing, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea, amaryllis, zinnia
1. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
3. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growsazalea##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who growsazalea is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is writing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing | writing | filmmaking |
| Flower   | amaryllis          | azalea     | zinnia  | aconite     |

