.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, r&b, country, salsa
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, sports
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of salsa is between the person watching sports movies and the fan of folk##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre           | folk | salsa | r&b | country     |
| Movie-Genre   | action   | documentary    | sports   | adventure |

