3. the librarian is on the right of the doctor##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Job           | doctor | librarian | firefighter | entrepreneur |
| Transport   | taxi   | bike | tram         | jet-ski |

