1. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the spanish is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the airplane and the italian##2
4. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | italian | egyptian | pakistani |
| Transport           | scooter  | car  | trike | airplane      |

