.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, australian, chinese, polish
City: new-york, prague, paris, marseilles
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the polish is the person traveling to new-york##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is between the american and the chinese##2
5. the chinese is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish   | american   | australian | chinese |
| City         | new-york | prague | marseilles     | paris    |

